# Autonomous — Maintainers

Governance model: BDFL, in the Linux tradition. Final decisions rest with the lead
maintainer, not a committee. See GOVERNANCE.md.

Lead maintainer:
  @deehw   (GitHub)   — contact: TBD

Subsystems (owner; path):
  OS core / managers        @deehw    os/core/
  HAL runtime + drivers     @deehw    os/hal/
  Board platform support    @deehw    os/hal/platform/
  Device contracts (frozen) @deehw    contract/, devices/
  Skills                    @deehw    skills/
  Web UI                    @deehw    os/web/

To propose a change, open a PR against the relevant subsystem and tag its owner.
Changes under contract/ are ABI changes and require lead-maintainer sign-off.
